    'photocell': '<strong>Integrated photocell ships standard on every Atlanta SKU</strong> \u2014 the <code>/PS</code> segment is part of every catalog number (<code>LWPA3W80-3A1-UD/PS</code> \u00B7 <code>LWPA3W120-3A1-UD/PS</code>), pre-installed and pre-wired at the factory. Automatic on at sundown, off at sunrise, dawn-to-dusk threshold tuned for outdoor perimeter applications. <strong>Skip the photocell when 1-10V control is already running</strong> to the perimeter \u2014 running both is redundant; in that case wire only the dim leads and let the photocell sit dormant. <strong>Optional motion / occupancy sensor variants</strong> available by model class \u2014 coordinate with the rep desk for the energy-code spec call (Title 24, ASHRAE 90.1, IECC).'
  };
  var LINK_LABEL = {
    'dimming':   'Discover 1-10V dimming \u2192',
    'photocell': 'Discover photocell + sensors \u2192'
  };

